en_155835_0	Police say that the mastermind behind the kalutara shooting that left 7 dead including underworld kingpin Samayang,  as well as the majority of accomplices have already been identified.
en_155835_1	Police Media spokesman DIG Priyantha Jayakody said a special operation has been initiated under the direct supervision of the IGP to arrest the suspects.
en_155835_2	He also said that special security has been put in place at the Katunayake and the Mattala airports to prevent the suspects from fleeing the country.
en_155835_3	Asenior officer stated that some used food packaging materials believed to have been left by the suspects and some blood samples collected from the crime scene will undergo DNA testing.
en_155835_4	Meanwhile, funerals for the jailor S.R. Wijerathna was held in Waadduwa yesterday. the funeral for the prison guard S. Sannigam will be held in Batticaloa today.
en_155835_5	Meanwhile, the final rites for Aruna Damith Udayanga aka Samayang was held yesterday.
en_155835_6	Funerals for the other  4 prisoners who died in the shooting will be held today in Korathota.
